<p>Search for pet-friendly hotels on <a href="https://www.expedia.ca/Hotel-Search?destination=Banff%2C+Alberta&camref=1101l3MtWX" target="_blank" rel="noopener sponsored">Expedia</a> using the pet filter.</p>

<h2>Essential Gear for Dogs in Banff</h2>
