<h2>Practical Tips for Fall Visitors</h2>
<ul>
<li><strong>Book larch season early:</strong> Moraine Lake shuttle reservations for late September sell out very fast. Accommodation fills quickly during peak larch weeks</li>
<li><strong>Carry bear spray:</strong> Bears are very active in fall. Bear encounters are more common as bears feed before hibernation</li>
