<p>A Canadian classic. These hand-stretched, fried dough pastries are topped with everything from cinnamon sugar and Nutella to maple butter and whipped cream. Find them on Banff Avenue during peak season. A Beaver Tail after a long hike is practically a Canadian rite of passage.</p>

<h3>Street Meat BBQ</h3>
